    <briefdescription>
<para>Debugging utilities for 28Cx EEPROM programmer firmware. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>EEPROM Programmer Firmware</para>
<para>Contains functions for debugging and testing the EEPROM programmer firmware. This may include functions for testing pin states, timing, and communication with the Python control script. These functions can be called from the main loop or setup to verify correct operation of the hardware and firmware. </para>
